    "Training was performed on Windows 10 with Python 3.12.3.",
    "Inference requires 4.1 × 10 -4 seconds per step using the same hardware.",
    "V. ConclusionsWe formulated a sparse indirect control problem and proposed an optimal learning-based solution.",
    "Using PPO, we trained a controller to minimize the L 2 error between the desired and expected steady-state density profiles while keeping the control effort low.",
